<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.10">
<l>niṉṟuruku kiṉṟēṉē pōla neṭuvāṉañ</l>
<l>ceṉṟuruki nuṇṭuḷiyāyccelkiṉṟa kaṅkulvā</l>
<l>yaṉṟorukāl vaiya maḷantapirāṉ vārāṉeṉ</l>
<l>ṟoṉṟorukāl collātulakō vuṟaṅkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like me standing [and] dissolving, does the long sky</l>
<l>go [and] dissolve, in fine drops, during the night that goes [on],</l>
<l>does the world slumber without saying even once</l>
<l>“the lord who measured the world with one foot that day will not come”?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
